  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654100/extras/66261df25e84d3d0f4ea3c562d858b1c.poster.avif?t=1748350776\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654100/extras/66261df25e84d3d0f4ea3c562d858b1c.webm?t=1748350776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654100/extras/66261df25e84d3d0f4ea3c562d858b1c.mp4?t=1748350776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Transform into your Mega Gunship boss form to blast your rival head-on in this unique shooting game with a competitive twist.<br><br>Rival Megagun is a competitive split-screen vertical shmup (or shoot 'em up, shooting game, STG) where you transform into a gigantic boss ship - your \"Mega Gunship\" - to invade your opponent's screen. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654100/extras/f0a26bcb07e7ef440a9b6f6659f16d36.poster.avif?t=1748350776\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654100/extras/f0a26bcb07e7ef440a9b6f6659f16d36.webm?t=1748350776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654100/extras/f0a26bcb07e7ef440a9b6f6659f16d36.mp4?t=1748350776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Classic shmup action with a competitive twist<br></li><li> Multiple playable heroes, each with their own special weapons and Mega Gunship boss form<br></li><li> Intense 2-player \"couch-competitive\" local versus battles<br></li><li> Online battles - challenge your friends or find opponents via matchmaking<br></li><li> Unlockable gear and weapons for customizing your ship<br></li><li> A single-player arcade mode</li></ul>",
